271//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
272void File__Analyze::Open_Buffer_Init (int64u File_Size_)
273{
274 //Preparing
275 File_Size=File_Size_;
276 Element[0].Next=File_Size;
277
278 //Buffer - Global
279 Read_Buffer_Init();
280
281 //Integrity
282 if (File_Offset>File_Size)
283 {
284 Reject();
285 return; //There is a problem
286 }
287
288 //Jump handling
289 if (File_GoTo!=(int64u)-1)
290 {
291 Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
292 File_GoTo=(int64u)-1;
293 }
294
295 //Configuring
296 if (MediaInfoLib::Config.FormatDetection_MaximumOffset_Get())
297 Buffer_TotalBytes_FirstSynched_Max=MediaInfoLib::Config.FormatDetection_MaximumOffset_Get();
298 Config->ParseSpeed=MediaInfoLib::Config.ParseSpeed_Get();
299 if (Config->File_IsSub_Get())
300 IsSub=true;
301 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
302 if (Demux_Level==1 && !IsSub && Config->Demux_Unpacketize_Get()) //If Demux_Level is Frame
303 {
304 Demux_Level=2; //Container
305 Demux_UnpacketizeContainer=true;
306 }
307 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
308 #if MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
309 if (StreamIDs_Size && IsRawStream)
310 StreamIDs[StreamIDs_Size-1]=(int64u)-1;
311 if (!IsSub)
312 {
313 ZtringListList SubFile_IDs;
314 SubFile_IDs.Separator_Set(0, EOL);
315 SubFile_IDs.Separator_Set(1, __T(","));
316 SubFile_IDs.Write(Config->SubFile_IDs_Get());
317 if (!SubFile_IDs.empty())
318 {
319 StreamIDs_Size=1+SubFile_IDs.size();
320 StreamIDs[SubFile_IDs.size()]=IsRawStream?(int64u)-1:StreamIDs[0];
321 StreamIDs_Width[SubFile_IDs.size()]=StreamIDs_Width[0];
322 ParserIDs[SubFile_IDs.size()]=ParserIDs[0];
323 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<SubFile_IDs.size(); Pos++)
324 {
325 StreamIDs[Pos]=SubFile_IDs[Pos](0).To_int64u();
326 StreamIDs_Width[Pos]=SubFile_IDs[Pos](1).To_int8u();
327 ParserIDs[Pos]=SubFile_IDs[Pos](2).To_int8u();
328 }
329 }
330 }
331 #endif //MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
332 #if MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
333 Config_Ibi_Create=Config->Ibi_Create_Get() && Config->ParseSpeed==1.0;
334 if (Config_Ibi_Create && !IsSub && IbiStream==NULL)
335 IbiStream=new ibi::stream;
336 #endif //MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
337}
338
339void File__Analyze::Open_Buffer_Init (File__Analyze* Sub)
340{
341 Open_Buffer_Init(Sub, File_Size);
342}
343
344void File__Analyze::Open_Buffer_Init (File__Analyze* Sub, int64u File_Size_)
345{
346 //Integrity
347 if (Sub==NULL
348 #if MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
349 || StreamIDs_Size==0
350 #endif
351 )
352 return;
353
354 //Parsing
355 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
356 Sub->Init(Config, Details);
357 #else //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
358 Sub->Init(Config);
359 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
360 #if MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
361 Sub->ParserIDs[StreamIDs_Size]=Sub->ParserIDs[0];
362 Sub->StreamIDs_Width[StreamIDs_Size]=Sub->StreamIDs_Width[0];
363 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<StreamIDs_Size; Pos++)
364 {
365 Sub->ParserIDs[Pos]=ParserIDs[Pos];
366 Sub->StreamIDs[Pos]=StreamIDs[Pos];
367 Sub->StreamIDs_Width[Pos]=StreamIDs_Width[Pos];
368 }
369 Sub->StreamIDs[StreamIDs_Size-1]=Element_Code;
370 Sub->StreamIDs_Size=StreamIDs_Size+1;
371 #endif //MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
372 Sub->IsSub=true;
373 Sub->File_Name_WithoutDemux=IsSub?File_Name_WithoutDemux:File_Name;
374 Sub->Open_Buffer_Init(File_Size_);
375}
376
377void File__Analyze::Open_Buffer_OutOfBand (File__Analyze* Sub, const int8u* ToAdd, size_t ToAdd_Size)
378{
379 if (Sub==NULL)
380 return;
381
382 //Sub
383 if (Sub->File_GoTo!=(int64u)-1)
384 Sub->File_GoTo=(int64u)-1;
385 Sub->File_Offset=File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset;
386 if (Sub->File_Size!=File_Size)
387 {
388 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<=Sub->Element_Level; Pos++)
389 if (Sub->Element[Pos].Next==Sub->File_Size)
390 Sub->Element[Pos].Next=File_Size;
391 Sub->File_Size=File_Size;
392 }
393 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
394 Sub->Element_Level_Base=Element_Level_Base+Element_Level;
395 #endif
396
397 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
398 bool Demux_EventWasSent_Save=Config->Demux_EventWasSent;
399 Config->Demux_EventWasSent=false;
400 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
401 Sub->Open_Buffer_OutOfBand(ToAdd, ToAdd_Size);
402 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
403 if (Demux_EventWasSent_Save)
404 Config->Demux_EventWasSent=true;
405 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
406
407 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
408 if (Trace_Activated)
409 {
410 //Details handling
411 if ((Sub->Element[0].TraceNode.Get_Name() || Sub->Element[0].TraceNode.Children.size()) && !Trace_DoNotSave)
412 {
413 //From Sub
414 while(Sub->Element_Level)
415 Sub->Element_End0();
416
417 //Add Sub to this node
418 Element[Element_Level].TraceNode.Add_Child(&Sub->Element[0].TraceNode);
419 Sub->Element[0].TraceNode.Init();
420 }
421 else
422 Element[Element_Level].TraceNode.NoShow=true; //We don't want to show this item because there is no info in it
423 }
424 #endif
425}
426
427//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
428void File__Analyze::Open_Buffer_Continue (const int8u* ToAdd, size_t ToAdd_Size)
429{
430 //Deleyed events
431 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
432 if (Config->Events_Delayed_CurrentSource)
433 {
434 File__Analyze* Temp=Config->Events_Delayed_CurrentSource;
435 Config->Events_Delayed_CurrentSource=NULL;
436 Config->Event_Accepted(Temp);
437 if (Config->Events_Delayed_CurrentSource)
438 return;
439 }
440 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
441
442 if (ToAdd_Size)
443 {
444 Frame_Count_InThisBlock=0;
445 Field_Count_InThisBlock=0;
446 }
447
448 //Hash
449 #if MEDIAINFO_HASH
450 if (ToAdd_Size)
451 {
452 if (!IsSub && !Buffer_Temp_Size && File_Offset==Config->File_Current_Offset && Config->File_Hash_Get().to_ulong())
453 {
454 delete Hash; Hash=new HashWrapper(Config->File_Hash_Get().to_ulong());
455 }
456 if (Hash)
457 Hash->Update(ToAdd, ToAdd_Size);
458 }
459 #endif //MEDIAINFO_HASH
460
461 //AES
462 #if MEDIAINFO_AES
463 if (ToAdd_Size)
464 {
465 if (!IsSub && !Buffer_Temp_Size && File_Offset==Config->File_Current_Offset
466 && Config->Encryption_Format_Get()==Encryption_Format_Aes
467 && Config->Encryption_Key_Get().size()==16
468 && Config->Encryption_Method_Get()==Encryption_Method_Segment
469 && Config->Encryption_Mode_Get()==Encryption_Mode_Cbc
470 && Config->Encryption_Padding_Get()==Encryption_Padding_Pkcs7
471 && Config->Encryption_InitializationVector_Get()=="Sequence number")
472 {
473 delete AES; AES=new AESdecrypt;
474 AES->key128((const unsigned char*)Config->Encryption_Key_Get().c_str());
475 AES_IV=new int8u[16];
476 int128u2BigEndian(AES_IV, int128u((int64u)Config->File_Names_Pos-1));
477 }
478 if (AES)
479 {
480 if (AES_Decrypted_Size<ToAdd_Size)
481 {
482 delete AES_Decrypted; AES_Decrypted=new int8u[ToAdd_Size*2];
483 AES_Decrypted_Size=ToAdd_Size*2;
484 }
485 AES->cbc_decrypt(ToAdd, AES_Decrypted, (int)ToAdd_Size, AES_IV); //TODO: handle the case where ToAdd_Size is more than 2GB
486 if (File_Offset+Buffer_Size+ToAdd_Size>=Config->File_Current_Size && ToAdd_Size)
487 {
488 int8u LastByte=AES_Decrypted[ToAdd_Size-1];
489 ToAdd_Size-=LastByte;
490 if (Config->File_Names_Pos && Config->File_Names_Pos-1<Config->File_Sizes.size())
491 Config->File_Sizes[Config->File_Names_Pos-1]-=LastByte;
492 Config->File_Current_Size-=LastByte;
493 }
494 ToAdd=AES_Decrypted;
495 }
496 }
497 #endif //MEDIAINFO_AES
498
499 //Integrity
500 if (Status[IsFinished])
501 return;
502 //{File F; F.Open(Ztring(__T("d:\\direct"))+Ztring::ToZtring((size_t)this, 16), File::Access_Write_Append); F.Write(ToAdd, ToAdd_Size);}
503
504 //Demand to go elsewhere
505 if (File_GoTo!=(int64u)-1)
506 {
507 if (File_GoTo<File_Offset)
508 return; //Seek must be done before
509 if (File_GoTo>=File_Offset+ToAdd_Size)
510 {
511 File_Offset+=ToAdd_Size;
512 return; //No need of this piece of data
513 }
514 }
515
516 #if MEDIAINFO_HASH
517 //Hash parsing only
518 if (Hash_ParseUpTo>File_Offset+Buffer_Size+ToAdd_Size)
519 {
520 File_Offset+=ToAdd_Size;
521 return; //No need of this piece of data
522 }
523 if (Hash_ParseUpTo>File_Offset && Hash_ParseUpTo<=File_Offset+ToAdd_Size)
524 {
525 Buffer_Offset+=(size_t)(Hash_ParseUpTo-File_Offset);
526 Hash_ParseUpTo=0;
527 }
528 #endif //MEDIAINFO_HASH
529
530 if (Buffer_Temp_Size) //There is buffered data from before
531 {
532 //Allocating new buffer if needed
533 if (Buffer_Temp_Size+ToAdd_Size>Buffer_Temp_Size_Max)
534 {
535 int8u* Old=Buffer_Temp;
536 size_t Buffer_Temp_Size_Max_ToAdd=ToAdd_Size>32768?ToAdd_Size:32768;
537 if (Buffer_Temp_Size_Max_ToAdd<Buffer_Temp_Size_Max) Buffer_Temp_Size_Max_ToAdd=Buffer_Temp_Size_Max;
538 Buffer_Temp_Size_Max+=Buffer_Temp_Size_Max_ToAdd;
539 Buffer_Temp=new int8u[Buffer_Temp_Size_Max];
540 memcpy_Unaligned_Unaligned(Buffer_Temp, Old, Buffer_Temp_Size);
541 delete[] Old; //Old=NULL;
542 }
543
544 //Copying buffer
545 if (ToAdd_Size>0)
546 {
547 memcpy_Unaligned_Unaligned(Buffer_Temp+Buffer_Size, ToAdd, ToAdd_Size);
548 Buffer_Temp_Size+=ToAdd_Size;
549 }
550
551 //Buffer
552 Buffer=Buffer_Temp;
553 Buffer_Size=Buffer_Temp_Size;
554 }
555 else
556 {
557 Buffer=ToAdd;
558 Buffer_Size=ToAdd_Size;
559 }
560
561 //Preparing
562 Trusted=(Buffer_Size>2*8*1024?Buffer_Size/8/1024:2)*Trusted_Multiplier; //Never less than 2 acceptable errors
563
564 //Demand to go elsewhere
565 if (File_GoTo!=(int64u)-1)
566 {
567 //The needed offset is in the new buffer
568 Buffer_Offset+=(size_t)(File_GoTo-File_Offset);
569 File_GoTo=(int64u)-1;
570 }
571
572 //Parsing
573 if (!IsSub)
574 {
575 if (Config->File_Size && Config->File_Size!=(int64u)-1)
576 Config->State_Set(((float)Buffer_TotalBytes)/Config->File_Size);
577 else if (Config->File_Names.size()>1)
578 Config->State_Set(((float)Config->File_Names_Pos)/Config->File_Names.size());
579 }
580 if (Buffer_Size>=Buffer_MinimumSize || File_Offset+Buffer_Size==File_Size) //Parsing only if we have enough buffer
581 while (Open_Buffer_Continue_Loop());
582
583 //Hash
584 #if MEDIAINFO_HASH
585 if (Hash_ParseUpTo>File_Size)
586 Hash_ParseUpTo=File_Size;
587
588 if (Hash && File_Offset+Buffer_Size>=Config->File_Current_Size && Status[IsAccepted])
589 {
590 for (size_t Hash_Pos=0; Hash_Pos<HashWrapper::HashFunction_Max; ++Hash_Pos)
591 {
592 string Hash_Name(HashWrapper::Name((HashWrapper::HashFunction)Hash_Pos));
593 Ztring Temp;
594 Temp.From_UTF8(Hash->Generate((HashWrapper::HashFunction)Hash_Pos));
595 string HashPos=Config->File_Names.size()>1?("Source_List_"+Hash_Name+"_Generated"):(Hash_Name+"_Generated");
596 if (Config->File_Names_Pos<=1 && !Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, HashPos.c_str()).empty() && Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, HashPos.c_str())==Temp)
597 Clear(Stream_General, 0, HashPos.c_str());
598 Fill(Stream_General, 0, HashPos.c_str(), Temp);
599 if (Config->File_Names_Pos<=1)
600 (*Stream_More)[Stream_General][0](Ztring().From_Local(HashPos), Info_Options)=__T("N NT");
601 }
602
603 delete Hash; Hash=NULL;
604 }
605
606 if (Hash && File_GoTo!=(int64u)-1)
607 {
608 delete Hash; Hash=NULL; //Hash not possible with a seek
609 }
610
611 if (Hash && Buffer_Offset>Buffer_Size)
612 {
613 //We need the next data
614 Hash_ParseUpTo=File_Offset+Buffer_Offset;
615 Buffer_Offset=Buffer_Size;
616 }
617 #endif //MEDIAINFO_HASH
618
619 //Should parse again?
620 if (((File_GoTo==File_Size && File_Size!=(int64u)-1) || File_Offset+Buffer_Offset>=File_Size)
621 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
622 && !Config->Demux_EventWasSent
623 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
624 )
625 {
626 BookMark_Get();
627
628 if (File_GoTo>=File_Size)
629 {
630 Element_Show(); //If Element_Level is >0, we must show what is in the details buffer
631 while (Element_Level>0)
632 Element_End0(); //This is Finish, must flush
633 Buffer_Clear();
634 File_Offset=File_Size;
635 if (!IsSub && !Config->File_Names.empty())
636 {
637 if (Config->File_Sizes.size()>=Config->File_Names.size())
638 Config->File_Current_Size=Config->File_Sizes[Config->File_Names.size()-1];
639 Config->File_Current_Offset=Config->File_Current_Size;
640 Config->File_Names_Pos=Config->File_Names.size()-1;
641 }
642 ForceFinish();
643 return;
644 }
645 }
646
647 //Demand to go elsewhere
648 if (File_GoTo!=(int64u)-1)
649 {
650 if (Config->File_IsSeekable_Get())
651 {
652 if (File_GoTo>=File_Size)
653 File_GoTo=File_Size;
654 Buffer_Clear();
655 }
656 else
657 File_Offset+=Buffer_Offset;
658
659 return;
660 }
661 #if MEDIAINFO_HASH
662 if (Hash_ParseUpTo)
663 {
664 Buffer_Clear();
665 return;
666 }
667 #endif //MEDIAINFO_HASH
668 if (Buffer_Offset>=Buffer_Size
669 #if MEDIAINFO_HASH
670 && Hash==NULL
671 #endif //MEDIAINFO_HASH
672 )
673 {
674 if (Buffer_Offset>Buffer_Size)
675 File_GoTo=File_Offset+Buffer_Offset;
676 Buffer_Clear();
677 return;
678 }
679
680 //Buffer handling
681 if (Buffer_Size && Buffer_Offset<=Buffer_Size) //all is not used
682 {
683 if (File_Offset+Buffer_Size>=File_Size //No more data will come
684 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
685 && !Config->Demux_EventWasSent
686 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
687 )
688 {
689 ForceFinish();
690 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
691 if (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
692 return;
693 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
694 }
695
696 if (Buffer_Temp_Size==0) //If there was no copy
697 {
698 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
699 if (!IsSub && Config->Demux_EventWasSent && Config->File_Buffer_Repeat_IsSupported && Buffer_Offset==0) //If there was no byte consumed
700 {
701 Config->File_Buffer_Repeat=true;
702 }
703 else
704 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
705 {
706 if (Buffer_Temp!=NULL && Buffer_Temp_Size_Max<ToAdd_Size-Buffer_Offset)
707 {
708 delete[] Buffer_Temp; Buffer_Temp=NULL; Buffer_Temp_Size=0; Buffer_Temp_Size_Max=0;
709 }
710 if (Buffer_Temp==NULL)
711 {
712 size_t Buffer_Temp_Size_Max_ToAdd=ToAdd_Size-Buffer_Offset>32768?ToAdd_Size-Buffer_Offset:32768;
713 if (Buffer_Temp_Size_Max_ToAdd<Buffer_Temp_Size_Max) Buffer_Temp_Size_Max_ToAdd=Buffer_Temp_Size_Max;
714 Buffer_Temp_Size_Max=Buffer_Temp_Size_Max_ToAdd;
715 Buffer_Temp=new int8u[Buffer_Temp_Size_Max];
716 }
717 Buffer_Temp_Size=ToAdd_Size-Buffer_Offset;
718 memcpy_Unaligned_Unaligned(Buffer_Temp, ToAdd+Buffer_Offset, Buffer_Temp_Size);
719 }
720 }
721 else if (Buffer_Offset) //Already a copy, just moving it
722 {
723 std::memmove(Buffer_Temp, Buffer_Temp+Buffer_Offset, Buffer_Size-Buffer_Offset);
724 Buffer_Temp_Size=Buffer_Size-Buffer_Offset;
725 }
726 }
727 else if (Buffer_Temp_Size)
728 Buffer_Temp_Size=0;
729
730 //Reserving unused data
731 if ((int64u)-1-Buffer_Offset<File_Offset) //In case of unknown filesize, File_Offset may be (int64u)-1
732 Buffer_Offset=(size_t)((int64u)-1-File_Offset);
733 if (Buffer_Offset)
734 {
735 if (Buffer_Offset>=FrameInfo.Buffer_Offset_End && FrameInfo_Next.DTS!=(int64u)-1)
736 {
737 FrameInfo=FrameInfo_Next;
738 FrameInfo_Next=frame_info();
739 }
740
741 float64 Ratio=1;
742 if (OriginalBuffer)
743 {
744 Ratio=((float64)OriginalBuffer_Size)/Buffer_Size;
745 size_t Temp_Size=(size_t)float64_int64s(((float64)Buffer_Offset)*Ratio);
746
747 OriginalBuffer_Size-=Temp_Size;
748 memmove(OriginalBuffer, OriginalBuffer+Buffer_Offset, OriginalBuffer_Size);
749 }
750
751 Buffer_Size-=Buffer_Offset;
752 File_Offset+=Buffer_Offset;
753 if (Buffer_Offset_Temp>=Buffer_Offset)
754 Buffer_Offset_Temp-=Buffer_Offset;
755 if (FrameInfo.Buffer_Offset_End!=(int64u)-1 && FrameInfo.Buffer_Offset_End>=Buffer_Offset)
756 FrameInfo.Buffer_Offset_End-=Buffer_Offset;
757 if (FrameInfo_Next.Buffer_Offset_End!=(int64u)-1 && FrameInfo_Next.Buffer_Offset_End>=Buffer_Offset)
758 FrameInfo_Next.Buffer_Offset_End-=Buffer_Offset;
759 if (!Offsets_Buffer.empty())
760 {
761 if (Offsets_Buffer.size()>=2 && Offsets_Buffer.size()%2==0 && Offsets_Buffer[0]==Offsets_Buffer[1])
762 {
763 size_t Pos=Offsets_Buffer.size()-2;
764 do
765 {
766 if (Offsets_Buffer[Pos]>Buffer_Offset)
767 {
768 Offsets_Buffer[Pos]-=Buffer_Offset;
769 Offsets_Buffer[Pos+1]-=Buffer_Offset;
770 }
771 else
772 {
773 Offsets_Stream[Pos]+=float64_int64s(Buffer_Offset*Ratio/2)-Offsets_Buffer[Pos];
774 Offsets_Stream[Pos+1]+=float64_int64s(Buffer_Offset*Ratio/2)-Offsets_Buffer[Pos+1];
775 Offsets_Buffer[Pos]=0;
776 Offsets_Buffer[Pos+1]=0;
777 Offsets_Buffer.erase(Offsets_Buffer.begin(), Offsets_Buffer.begin()+Pos);
778 Offsets_Stream.erase(Offsets_Stream.begin(), Offsets_Stream.begin()+Pos);
779 if (Offsets_Pos!=(size_t)-1 && Pos)
780 {
781 if (Pos<Offsets_Pos)
782 Offsets_Pos-=Pos;
783 else
784 Offsets_Pos=0;
785 }
786 break;
787 }
788 if (Pos==0)
789 break;
790 Pos-=2;
791 }
792 while (Pos);
793 }
794 else
795 {
796 size_t Pos=Offsets_Buffer.size()-1;
797 do
798 {
799 if (Offsets_Buffer[Pos]>Buffer_Offset*Ratio)
800 Offsets_Buffer[Pos]-=float64_int64s(Buffer_Offset*Ratio);
801 else
802 {
803 Offsets_Stream[Pos]+=float64_int64s(Buffer_Offset*Ratio)-Offsets_Buffer[Pos];
804 Offsets_Buffer[Pos]=0;
805 Offsets_Buffer.erase(Offsets_Buffer.begin(), Offsets_Buffer.begin()+Pos);
806 Offsets_Stream.erase(Offsets_Stream.begin(), Offsets_Stream.begin()+Pos);
807 if (Offsets_Pos!=(size_t)-1 && Pos)
808 {
809 if (Pos<Offsets_Pos)
810 Offsets_Pos-=Pos;
811 else
812 Offsets_Pos=0;
813 }
814 break;
815 }
816 if (Pos==0)
817 break;
818 Pos--;
819 }
820 while (Pos);
821 }
822 }
823
824 Buffer_Offset=0;
825 }
826
827 //Is it OK?
828 if (Buffer_Size>Buffer_MaximumSize)
829 {
830 #if MEDIAINFO_HASH
831 if (Config->File_Hash_Get().to_ulong() && Hash && Status[IsAccepted])
832 {
833 Buffer_Clear();
834 Hash_ParseUpTo=File_Size;
835 }
836 else
837 #endif //MEDIAINFO_HASH
838 ForceFinish();
839 return;
840 }
841}
842
843void File__Analyze::Open_Buffer_Continue (File__Analyze* Sub, const int8u* ToAdd, size_t ToAdd_Size, bool IsNewPacket, float64 Ratio)
844{
845 if (Sub==NULL)
846 return;
847
848 //Sub
849 if (Sub->File_GoTo!=(int64u)-1)
850 Sub->File_GoTo=(int64u)-1;
851 Sub->File_Offset=File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset;
852 if (Sub->File_Size!=File_Size)
853 {
854 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<=Sub->Element_Level; Pos++)
855 if (Sub->Element[Pos].Next==Sub->File_Size)
856 Sub->Element[Pos].Next=File_Size;
857 Sub->File_Size=File_Size;
858 }
859 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
860 Sub->Element_Level_Base=Element_Level_Base+Element_Level;
861 #endif
862
863 //{File F; F.Open(Ztring(__T("d:\\direct"))+Ztring::ToZtring((size_t)this, 16), File::Access_Write_Append); F.Write(ToAdd, ToAdd_Size);}
864
865 //Adaptating File_Offset
866 if (Sub!=this && Sub->Buffer_Size<=Sub->File_Offset)
867 Sub->File_Offset-=Sub->Buffer_Size;
868
869 //Parsing
870 Sub->PES_FirstByte_IsAvailable=PES_FirstByte_IsAvailable;
871 Sub->PES_FirstByte_Value=PES_FirstByte_Value;
872 if (IsNewPacket && ToAdd_Size)
873 {
874 if (Offsets_Stream.empty())
875 {
876 Sub->Offsets_Stream.push_back(File_Offset+float64_int64s((Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset)*Ratio));
877 Sub->Offsets_Buffer.push_back(Sub->Buffer_Size);
878 }
879 else
880 {
881 if (Offsets_Buffer[0]>=Buffer_Offset-Header_Size && (Sub->Offsets_Stream.empty() || Sub->Offsets_Stream[Sub->Offsets_Stream.size()-1]+Sub->Buffer_Size-Sub->Offsets_Buffer[Sub->Offsets_Stream.size()-1]!=Offsets_Stream[0]))
882 {
883 if ((Buffer_Offset-Header_Size)*Ratio<Offsets_Buffer[0])
884 {
885 Sub->Offsets_Stream.push_back(Offsets_Stream[0]);
886 Sub->Offsets_Buffer.push_back((Sub->OriginalBuffer_Size?Sub->OriginalBuffer_Size:Sub->Buffer_Size)+Offsets_Buffer[0]-(Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset));
887 }
888 else
889 {
890 Sub->Offsets_Stream.push_back(Offsets_Stream[0]+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset-Offsets_Buffer[0]);
891 Sub->Offsets_Buffer.push_back(Sub->OriginalBuffer_Size?Sub->OriginalBuffer_Size:Sub->Buffer_Size);
892 }
893 }
894 for (size_t Pos=1; Pos<Offsets_Stream.size(); Pos++)
895 if (Offsets_Buffer[Pos]>=Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset && Offsets_Buffer[Pos]<Buffer_Offset+Element_Size)
896 {
897 if ((Buffer_Offset-Header_Size)*Ratio<Offsets_Buffer[Pos])
898 {
899 Sub->Offsets_Stream.push_back(Offsets_Stream[Pos]);
900 Sub->Offsets_Buffer.push_back((Sub->OriginalBuffer_Size?Sub->OriginalBuffer_Size:Sub->Buffer_Size)+Offsets_Buffer[Pos]-(Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset));
901 }
902 else
903 {
904 Sub->Offsets_Stream.push_back(Offsets_Stream[Pos]+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset-Offsets_Buffer[Pos]);
905 Sub->Offsets_Buffer.push_back(Sub->OriginalBuffer_Size?Sub->OriginalBuffer_Size:Sub->Buffer_Size);
906 }
907 }
908 }
909 }
910
911 if (Ratio!=1)
912 {
913 if (Sub->OriginalBuffer_Size+Element_Size-Element_Offset>Sub->OriginalBuffer_Capacity)
914 {
915 int8u* Temp=Sub->OriginalBuffer;
916 Sub->OriginalBuffer_Capacity=(size_t)(Sub->OriginalBuffer_Size+Element_Size-Element_Offset);
917 Sub->OriginalBuffer=new int8u[Sub->OriginalBuffer_Capacity];
918 memcpy_Unaligned_Unaligned(Sub->OriginalBuffer, Temp, Sub->OriginalBuffer_Size);
919 delete[] Temp;
920 }
921 memcpy_Unaligned_Unaligned(Sub->OriginalBuffer+Sub->OriginalBuffer_Size, Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset, (size_t)(Element_Size-Element_Offset));
922 Sub->OriginalBuffer_Size+=(size_t)(Element_Size-Element_Offset);
923 }
924
925 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
926 if (Frequency_c)
927 Sub->Frequency_c=Frequency_c;
928 #endif //MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
929 if (Sub->FrameInfo.DTS!=(int64u)-1)
930 Sub->FrameInfo.Buffer_Offset_End=Sub->Buffer_Offset+Sub->Buffer_Size+ToAdd_Size;
931 else if (Sub->FrameInfo_Previous.DTS!=(int64u)-1)
932 Sub->FrameInfo_Previous.Buffer_Offset_End=Sub->Buffer_Offset+Sub->Buffer_Size+ToAdd_Size;
933 if (Sub->FrameInfo_Previous.DTS!=(int64u)-1)
934 {
935 Sub->FrameInfo_Next=Sub->FrameInfo;
936 Sub->FrameInfo=Sub->FrameInfo_Previous;
937 Sub->FrameInfo_Previous=frame_info();
938
939 Sub->Frame_Count_Previous=Sub->Frame_Count;
940 Sub->Field_Count_Previous=Sub->Field_Count;
941 }
942 if (Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded!=(int64u)-1)
943 Sub->Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded=Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded;
944 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
945 bool Demux_EventWasSent_Save=Config->Demux_EventWasSent;
946 Config->Demux_EventWasSent=false;
947 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
948 Sub->Open_Buffer_Continue(ToAdd, ToAdd_Size);
949 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
950 if (Demux_EventWasSent_Save)
951 Config->Demux_EventWasSent=true;
952 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
953 if (Sub->Buffer_Size)
954 {
955 Sub->FrameInfo_Previous=Sub->FrameInfo;
956 Sub->FrameInfo=Sub->FrameInfo_Next;
957 Sub->FrameInfo_Next=frame_info();
958 }
959
960 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
961 if (Trace_Activated)
962 {
963 //Details handling
964 if ((Sub->Element[0].TraceNode.Get_Name() || Sub->Element[0].TraceNode.Children.size()) && !Trace_DoNotSave)
965 {
966 //From Sub
967 while(Sub->Element_Level)
968 Sub->Element_End0();
969 Element[Element_Level].TraceNode.Add_Child(&Sub->Element[0].TraceNode);
970 Sub->Element[0].TraceNode.Init();
971 }
972 else
973 Element[Element_Level].TraceNode.NoShow=true; //We don't want to show this item because there is no info in it
974 }
975 #endif
976}

978//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
979bool File__Analyze::Open_Buffer_Continue_Loop ()
980{
981 //Header
982 if (MustParseTheHeaderFile)
983 {
984 if (!FileHeader_Manage())
985 return false; //Wait for more data
986 if (Status[IsFinished] || File_GoTo!=(int64u)-1)
987 return false; //Finish
988 }
989
990 //Parsing specific
991 Element_Offset=0;
992 Element_Size=Buffer_Size;
993 Element[Element_Level].WaitForMoreData=false;
994 Read_Buffer_Continue();
995 if (Element_IsWaitingForMoreData())
996 return false; //Wait for more data
997 if (sizeof(size_t)<sizeof(int64u) && Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset>=(int64u)(size_t)-1)
998 GoTo(File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset);
999 else
1000 Buffer_Offset+=(size_t)Element_Offset;
1001 if ((Status[IsFinished] && !ShouldContinueParsing) || Buffer_Offset>Buffer_Size || File_GoTo!=(int64u)-1)
1002 return false; //Finish
1003 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1004 if (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
1005 return false;
1006 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1007
1008 //Parsing;
1009 while (Buffer_Offset<Buffer_Size)
1010 if (!Buffer_Parse())
1011 break;
1012 Buffer_TotalBytes+=Buffer_Offset;
1013
1014 //Handling of File_GoTo with already buffered data
1015 #if MEDIAINFO_HASH
1016 if (File_GoTo==(int64u)-1 && Hash_ParseUpTo && Hash_ParseUpTo>=File_Offset && Hash_ParseUpTo<File_Offset+Buffer_Size)
1017 {
1018 File_GoTo=Hash_ParseUpTo;
1019 Hash_ParseUpTo=0;
1020 }
1021 #endif //MEDIAINFO_HASH
1022 if (File_GoTo!=(int64u)-1 && File_GoTo>=File_Offset && File_GoTo<File_Offset+Buffer_Size)
1023 {
1024 if (Buffer_Temp_Size==0) //If there was no copy
1025 {
1026 Buffer_Temp_Size=(size_t)(File_Offset+Buffer_Size-File_GoTo);
1027 if (Buffer_Temp!=NULL && Buffer_Temp_Size_Max<Buffer_Temp_Size)
1028 {
1029 delete[] Buffer_Temp; Buffer_Temp=NULL; Buffer_Temp_Size=0; Buffer_Temp_Size_Max=0;
1030 }
1031 if (Buffer_Temp==NULL)
1032 {
1033 size_t Buffer_Temp_Size_Max_ToAdd=Buffer_Temp_Size>32768?Buffer_Temp_Size:32768;
1034 if (Buffer_Temp_Size_Max_ToAdd<Buffer_Temp_Size_Max) Buffer_Temp_Size_Max_ToAdd=Buffer_Temp_Size_Max;
1035 Buffer_Temp_Size_Max=Buffer_Temp_Size_Max_ToAdd;
1036 Buffer_Temp=new int8u[Buffer_Temp_Size_Max];
1037 }
1038 memcpy_Unaligned_Unaligned(Buffer_Temp, Buffer+Buffer_Size-Buffer_Temp_Size, Buffer_Temp_Size);
1039 }
1040 else //Already a copy, just moving it
1041 {
1042 Buffer_Temp_Size=(size_t)(File_Offset+Buffer_Size-File_GoTo);
1043 std::memmove(Buffer_Temp, Buffer+Buffer_Size-Buffer_Temp_Size, Buffer_Temp_Size);
1044 }
1045 File_Offset+=Buffer_Size-Buffer_Temp_Size;
1046 Buffer=Buffer_Temp;
1047 Buffer_Offset=0;
1048 Buffer_Size=Buffer_Temp_Size;
1049 File_GoTo=(int64u)-1;
1050
1051 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1052 if (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
1053 return false;
1054 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1055
1056 return true;
1057 }
1058
1059 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1060 if (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
1061 return false;
1062 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1063
1064 //Parsing specific
1065 Read_Buffer_AfterParsing();
1066
1067 //Jumping to the end of the file if needed
1068 if (!IsSub && !EOF_AlreadyDetected && Config->ParseSpeed<1 && Count_Get(Stream_General))
1069 {
1070 Element[Element_Level].WaitForMoreData=false;
1071 Detect_EOF();
1072 if ((File_GoTo!=(int64u)-1 && File_GoTo>File_Offset+Buffer_Offset) || (Status[IsFinished] && !ShouldContinueParsing))
1073 {
1074 EOF_AlreadyDetected=true;
1075 return false;
1076 }
1077 }
1078
1079 return false;
1080}

1117//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1118void File__Analyze::Open_Buffer_Unsynch ()
1119{
1120 Status[IsFinished]=false;
1121 FrameInfo=frame_info();
1122 FrameInfo_Previous=frame_info();
1123 FrameInfo_Next=frame_info();
1124 Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded=Unsynch_Frame_Count;
1125 Unsynch_Frame_Count=(int64u)-1;
1126 PTS_End=0;
1127 DTS_End=0;
1128 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1129 Demux_IntermediateItemFound=true;
1130 Demux_Offset=0;
1131 Demux_TotalBytes=Buffer_TotalBytes;
1132 Config->Demux_EventWasSent=false;
1133 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1134
1135 //Clearing duration
1136 if (Synched)
1137 {
1138 for (size_t StreamKind=(size_t)Stream_General; StreamKind<(size_t)Stream_Menu; StreamKind++)
1139 {
1140 size_t StreamPos_Count=Count_Get((stream_t)StreamKind);
1141 for (size_t StreamPos=0; StreamPos<StreamPos_Count; StreamPos++)
1142 Clear((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter((stream_t)StreamKind, Generic_Duration));
1143 }
1144 }
1145
1146 //if (Synched)
1147 if (!MustSynchronize || File_Offset_FirstSynched!=(int64u)-1) //Synched at least once
1148 {
1149 Synched=false;
1150 UnSynched_IsNotJunk=true;
1151 Read_Buffer_Unsynched();
1152 Ibi_Read_Buffer_Unsynched();
1153 }
1154 Buffer_Clear();
1155
1156 //Some default values
1157 if (IsRawStream && File_GoTo==0)
1158 {
1159 FrameInfo.DTS=0;
1160 Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded=0;
1161 }
1162
1163 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
1164 PTSb=NoTs;
1165 DTSb=NoTs;
1166 #endif //MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
1167}

1173 Streams_Update();
1174
1175 Status[File__Analyze::IsUpdated]=false;
1176 for (size_t Pos=File__Analyze::User_16; Pos<File__Analyze::User_16+16; Pos++)
1177 Status[Pos]=false;
1178}

1180//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1181void File__Analyze::Open_Buffer_Finalize (bool NoBufferModification)
1182{
1183 //File with unknown size (stream...), finnishing
1184 if (!NoBufferModification && File_Size==(int64u)-1)
1185 {
1186 File_Size=File_Offset+Buffer_Size;
1187 Open_Buffer_Continue((const int8u*)NULL, 0);
1188 }
1189
1190 //Element must be Finish
1191 while (Element_Level>0)
1192 Element_End0();
1193
1194 //Buffer - Global
1195 Fill();
1196 if (!NoBufferModification)
1197 {
1198 ForceFinish();
1199 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1200 if (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
1201 return;
1202 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1203 Buffer_Clear();
1204 }
1205
1206 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
1207 if (Details && Details->empty())
1208 {
1209 Element[0].TraceNode.Print(Config_Trace_Format, *Details);
1210 if (Config_LineSeparator != __T("\n"))
1211 {
1212 Ztring Temp;
1213 Temp.From_UTF8(*Details);
1214 Temp.FindAndReplace(__T("\n"), Config_LineSeparator, 0, Ztring_Recursive);
1215 *Details=Temp.To_UTF8();
1216 }
1217 }
1218 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
1219
1220 #if MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
1221 if (Status[IsAccepted])
1222 {
1223 EVENT_BEGIN (General, End, 0)
1224 if (Event.StreamIDs_Size>=1)
1225 Event.StreamIDs[Event.StreamIDs_Size-1]=(int64u)-1;
1226 Event.PCR=(int64u)-1;
1227 Event.DTS=(int64u)-1;
1228 Event.PTS=(int64u)-1;
1229 Event.DUR=(int64u)-1;
1230 Event.Stream_Bytes_Analyzed=Buffer_TotalBytes;
1231 Event.Stream_Size=File_Size;
1232 Event.Stream_Bytes_Padding=Buffer_PaddingBytes;
1233 Event.Stream_Bytes_Junk=Buffer_JunkBytes;
1234 if (!IsSub && MustSynchronize && !Synched && !UnSynched_IsNotJunk)
1235 Event.Stream_Bytes_Junk+=Buffer_TotalBytes+Buffer_Offset-Buffer_TotalBytes_LastSynched;
1236 EVENT_END ()
1237 }
1238 #endif //MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
1239}

1241void File__Analyze::Open_Buffer_Finalize (File__Analyze* Sub)
1242{
1243 if (Sub==NULL)
1244 return;
1245
1246 //Finalize
1247 Open_Buffer_Init(Sub);
1248 Sub->Open_Buffer_Finalize();
1249}

1255//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1256#if MEDIAINFO_SEEK
1257size_t File__Analyze::Read_Buffer_Seek (size_t Method, int64u Value, int64u ID)
1258{
1259 #if MEDIAINFO_IBI
1260 if (!IsSub)
1261 {
1262 size_t ReturnValue=Ibi_Read_Buffer_Seek(Method, Value, ID);
1263 if (ReturnValue!=(size_t)-1) // If IBI file is supported
1264 return ReturnValue;
1265 }
1266 #endif //MEDIAINFO_IBI
1267
1268 //Parsing
1269 switch (Method)
1270 {
1271 case 0 : //Default stream seek (byte offset)
1272 GoTo(Value);
1273 Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
1274 return 1;
1275 case 1 : //Default stream seek (percentage)
1276 GoTo(File_Size*Value/10000);
1277 Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
1278 return 1;
1279 default :
1280 return (size_t)-1; //Not supported
1281 }
1282}
1283#endif //MEDIAINFO_SEEK

1285//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1286#if MEDIAINFO_SEEK
1287size_t File__Analyze::Read_Buffer_Seek_OneFramePerFile (size_t Method, int64u Value, int64u ID)
1288{
1289 //Parsing
1290 switch (Method)
1291 {
1292 case 0 :
1293 {
1294 if (Value>=Config->File_Size)
1295 return 2; //Invalid value
1296 int64u Offset=0;
1297 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Config->File_Sizes.size(); Pos++)
1298 {
1299 Offset+=Config->File_Sizes[Pos];
1300 if (Offset>=Value)
1301 {
1302 Offset-=Config->File_Sizes[Pos];
1303 break;
1304 }
1305 }
1306 GoTo(Offset);
1307 Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
1308 return 1;
1309 }
1310 case 1 :
1311 {
1312 if (Value>=10000)
1313 return 2; //Invalid value
1314 size_t FilePos=(size_t)((((float32)Value)/10000)*Config->File_Sizes.size());
1315 int64u Offset=0;
1316 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<FilePos; Pos++)
1317 Offset+=Config->File_Sizes[Pos];
1318 GoTo(Offset);
1319 Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
1320 return 1;
1321 }
1322 case 2 : //Timestamp
1323 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1324 if (Config->Demux_Rate_Get()==0)
1325 return (size_t)-1; //Not supported
1326 Value=float64_int64s(((float64)Value)/1000000000*Config->Demux_Rate_Get());
1327 #else //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1328 return (size_t)-1; //Not supported
1329 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1330 case 3 : //FrameNumber
1331 {
1332 if (Value>=Config->File_Names.size())
1333 return 2; //Invalid value
1334 int64u Offset=0;
1335 if (Config->File_Sizes.size()!=Config->File_Names.size())
1336 {
1337 Offset=Value; //File_GoTo is the frame offset in that case
1338 Config->File_GoTo_IsFrameOffset=true;
1339 }
1340 else
1341 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Value; Pos++)
1342 Offset+=Config->File_Sizes[Pos];
1343 GoTo(Offset);
1344 Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
1345 return 1;
1346 }
1347 default : return (size_t)-1; //Not supported
1348 }
1349}
1350#endif //MEDIAINFO_SEEK
1351
1352//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1353void File__Analyze::Read_Buffer_Unsynched_OneFramePerFile()
1354{
1355 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
1356 if (Config->File_Sizes.size()!=Config->File_Names.size())
1357 {
1358 Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded=File_GoTo;
1359 }
1360 else
1361 #endif //MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
1362 {
1363 int64u GoTo=File_GoTo;
1364 for (Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded=0; Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded<Config->File_Sizes.size(); Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded++)
1365 {
1366 if (GoTo>=Config->File_Sizes[(size_t)Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded])
1367 GoTo-=Config->File_Sizes[(size_t)Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded];
1368 else
1369 break;
1370 }
1371 }
1372
1373 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1374 if (!IsSub && Config->Demux_Rate_Get()) //TODO: remove !IsSub when time code delay is removed from PTS
1375 {
1376 FrameInfo.DTS=float64_int64s(Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded*((float64)1000000000)/Config->Demux_Rate_Get());
1377 FrameInfo.PTS=FrameInfo.DTS;
1378 }
1379 else
1380 FrameInfo.PTS=FrameInfo.DTS=(int64u)-1;
1381 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1382}
1383
1384//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1385bool File__Analyze::Buffer_Parse()
1386{
1387 //End of this level?
1388 if (File_Offset+Buffer_Offset>=Element[Element_Level].Next)
1389 {
1390 //There is no loop handler, so we make the level down here
1391 while (Element_Level>0 && File_Offset+Buffer_Offset>=Element[Element_Level].Next)
1392 Element_End0(); //This is a buffer restart, must sync to Element level
1393 if (File_Offset+Buffer_Offset==File_Size)
1394 return false; //End of file
1395 MustUseAlternativeParser=false; //Reset it if we go out of an element
1396 }
1397
1398 //Synchro
1399 if (MustSynchronize)
1400 do
1401 {
1402 if (!Synchro_Manage())
1403 return false; //Wait for more data
1404 }
1405 while (!Synched);
1406 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1407 else if (Demux_TotalBytes<=Buffer_TotalBytes+Buffer_Offset)
1408 {
1409 if (Demux_UnpacketizeContainer && !Demux_UnpacketizeContainer_Test())
1410 {
1411 Demux_Offset-=Buffer_Offset;
1412 return false; //Wait for more data
1413 }
1414 if (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
1415 return false;
1416 }
1417 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1418
1419 //Offsets
1420 if (Offsets_Pos==(size_t)-1 && !Offsets_Buffer.empty())
1421 Offsets_Pos=0;
1422 if (Offsets_Pos!=(size_t)-1)
1423 {
1424 while (Offsets_Pos<Offsets_Buffer.size() && Buffer_Offset>Offsets_Buffer[Offsets_Pos])
1425 Offsets_Pos++;
1426 if (Offsets_Pos>=Offsets_Buffer.size() || Buffer_Offset!=Offsets_Buffer[Offsets_Pos])
1427 Offsets_Pos--;
1428 }
1429
1430 //Header
1431 if (!Header_Manage())
1432 return false; //Wait for more data
1433
1434 //Data
1435 if (!Data_Manage())
1436 return false; //Wait for more data
1437
1438 Buffer_TotalBytes_LastSynched=Buffer_TotalBytes+Buffer_Offset;
1439
1440 return true;
1441}

1444void File__Analyze::Buffer_Clear()
1445{
1446 //Buffer
1447 BS->Attach(NULL, 0);
1448 delete[] Buffer_Temp; Buffer_Temp=NULL;
1449 if (!Status[IsFinished])
1450 File_Offset+=Buffer_Size;
1451 else
1452 {
1453 File_Offset=File_Size;
1454 if (!IsSub && !Config->File_Names.empty())
1455 {
1456 if (Config->File_Sizes.size()>=Config->File_Names.size())
1457 Config->File_Current_Size=Config->File_Sizes[Config->File_Names.size()-1];
1458 Config->File_Current_Offset=Config->File_Current_Size;
1459 Config->File_Names_Pos=Config->File_Names.size()-1;
1460 }
1461 }
1462 Buffer_Size=0;
1463 Buffer_Temp_Size=0;
1464 Buffer_Offset=0;
1465 Buffer_Offset_Temp=0;
1466 Buffer_MinimumSize=0;
1467
1468 OriginalBuffer_Size=0;
1469 Offsets_Stream.clear();
1470 Offsets_Buffer.clear();
1471 Offsets_Pos=(size_t)-1;
1472
1473 //Details
1474 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
1475 Element[Element_Level].WaitForMoreData=false; //We must finalize the details
1476 Element[Element_Level].IsComplete=true; //We must finalize the details
1477 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
1478
1479}

1485//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1486bool File__Analyze::Synchronize_0x000001()
1487{
1488 //Synchronizing
1489 while(Buffer_Offset+3<=Buffer_Size && (Buffer[Buffer_Offset ]!=0x00
1490 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+1]!=0x00
1491 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+2]!=0x01))
1492 {
1493 Buffer_Offset+=2;
1494 while(Buffer_Offset<Buffer_Size && Buffer[Buffer_Offset]!=0x00)
1495 Buffer_Offset+=2;
1496 if ((Buffer_Offset<Buffer_Size && Buffer[Buffer_Offset-1]==0x00) || Buffer_Offset>=Buffer_Size)
1497 Buffer_Offset--;
1498 }
1499
1500 //Parsing last bytes if needed
1501 if (Buffer_Offset+3==Buffer_Size && (Buffer[Buffer_Offset ]!=0x00
1502 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+1]!=0x00
1503 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+2]!=0x01))
1504 Buffer_Offset++;
1505 if (Buffer_Offset+2==Buffer_Size && (Buffer[Buffer_Offset ]!=0x00
1506 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+1]!=0x00))
1507 Buffer_Offset++;
1508 if (Buffer_Offset+1==Buffer_Size && Buffer[Buffer_Offset ]!=0x00)
1509 Buffer_Offset++;
1510
1511 if (Buffer_Offset+3>Buffer_Size)
1512 return false;
1513
1514 //Synched is OK
1515 Synched=true;
1516 return true;
1517}
1518
1519//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1520bool File__Analyze::FileHeader_Begin_0x000001()
1521{
1522 //Element_Size
1523 if (Buffer_Size<192*4)
1524 return true; //Not enough buffer for a test
1525
1526 //Detecting OldDirac/WAV/SWF/FLV/ELF/DPG/WM files
1527 int64u Magic8=CC8(Buffer);
1528 int32u Magic4=Magic8>>32;
1529 int32u Magic3=Magic4>> 8;
1530 int16u Magic2=Magic4>>16;
1531 if (Magic8==0x4B572D4449524143LL || Magic4==0x52494646 || Magic3==0x465753 || Magic3==0x464C56 || Magic4==0x7F454C46 || Magic4==0x44504730 || Magic4==0x3026B275 || Magic2==0x4D5A || Magic4==0x1A45DFA3)
1532 {
1533 Reject();
1534 return false;
1535 }
1536
1537 //GXF
1538 if (CC5(Buffer)==0x0000000001 && CC2(Buffer+14)==0xE1E2)
1539 {
1540 Reject();
1541 return false;
1542 }
1543
1544 //Detecting MPEG-4 files (ftyp/mdat/skip/free)
1545 Magic4=CC4(Buffer+4);
1546 switch (Magic4)
1547 {
1548 case 0x66747970 : //ftyp
1549 case 0x6D646174 : //mdat
1550 case 0x736B6970 : //skip
1551 case 0x66726565 : //free
1552 Reject();
1553 return false;
1554 default : break;
1555 }
1556
1557 //Detect TS files, and the parser is not enough precise to detect them later
1558 size_t Buffer_Offset=0;
1559 while (Buffer_Offset<188 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset]!=0x47) //Look for first Sync word
1560 Buffer_Offset++;
1561 if (Buffer_Offset<188 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188]==0x47 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188*2]==0x47 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188*3]==0x47)
1562 {
1563 Status[IsFinished]=true;
1564 return false;
1565 }
1566 Buffer_Offset=0;
1567
1568 //Detect BDAV files, and the parser is not enough precise to detect them later
1569 while (Buffer_Offset<192 && CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+4)!=0x47) //Look for first Sync word
1570 Buffer_Offset++;
1571 if (Buffer_Offset<192 && CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+192+4)==0x47 && CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+192*2+4)==0x47 && CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+192*3+4)==0x47)
1572 {
1573 Status[IsFinished]=true;
1574 return false;
1575 }
1576 Buffer_Offset=0;
1577
1578 //All should be OK...
1579 return true;
1580}
1581
1582//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1583bool File__Analyze::FileHeader_Begin_XML(XMLDocument &Document)
1584{
1585 //Element_Size
1586 if (!IsSub && (File_Size<32 || File_Size>16*1024*1024))
1587 {
1588 Reject();
1589 return false; //XML files are not expected to be so big
1590 }
1591
1592 //Element_Size
1593 if (!IsSub && Buffer_Size<File_Size)
1594 {
1595 Element_WaitForMoreData();
1596 return false; //Must wait for more data
1597 }
1598
1599 //XML header
1600 Ztring Data;
1601 if ((Buffer[0]=='<'
1602 && Buffer[1]==0x00)
1603 || (Buffer[0]==0xFF
1604 && Buffer[1]==0xFE
1605 && Buffer[2]=='<'
1606 && Buffer[3]==0x00))
1607 Data.From_UTF16LE((const char*)Buffer, Buffer_Size);
1608 else if ((Buffer[0]==0x00
1609 && Buffer[1]=='<')
1610 || (Buffer[0]==0xFE
1611 && Buffer[1]==0xFF
1612 && Buffer[2]==0x00
1613 && Buffer[3]=='<'))
1614 Data.From_UTF16BE((const char*)Buffer, Buffer_Size);
1615 else if ((Buffer[0]=='<')
1616 || (Buffer[0]==0xEF
1617 && Buffer[1]==0xBB
1618 && Buffer[2]==0xBF
1619 && Buffer[3]=='<'))
1620 Data.From_UTF8((const char*)Buffer, Buffer_Size);
1621 else
1622 {
1623 Reject();
1624 return false;
1625 }
1626
1627 string DataUTF8=Data.To_UTF8();
1628 if (Document.Parse(DataUTF8.c_str()))
1629 {
1630 Reject();
1631 return false;
1632 }
1633
1634 return true;
1635}

1662//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1663void File__Analyze::TS_Set(int64s Ticks, ts_type Type)
1664{
1665 if (IsRawStream)
1666 {
1667 if (!Frequency_b)
1668 return;
1669
1670 int64s divisor = gcd(1000000000, Frequency_b);
1671 if (Type&TS_PTS)
1672 FrameInfo.PTS=Ticks*(1000000000/divisor)/(Frequency_b/divisor);
1673 if (Type&TS_DTS)
1674 FrameInfo.DTS=Ticks*(1000000000/divisor)/(Frequency_b/divisor);
1675 }
1676 else
1677 {
1678 if (!Frequency_c)
1679 return;
1680
1681 int64s divisor = gcd(1000000000, Frequency_c);
1682 if (Type&TS_PTS)
1683 FrameInfo.PTS=Ticks*(1000000000/divisor)/(Frequency_c/divisor);
1684 if (Type&TS_DTS)
1685 FrameInfo.DTS=Ticks*(1000000000/divisor)/(Frequency_c/divisor);
1686 }
1687
1688#if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
1689 if (IsRawStream)
1690 {
1691 if (!Frequency_b)
1692 return;
1693
1694 if (Type&TS_PTS)
1695 PTSb=Ticks;
1696 if (Type&TS_DTS)
1697 DTSb=Ticks;
1698 if (Frequency_c)
1699 {
1700 if (Type&TS_PTS)
1701 PTSb*=Frequency_c;
1702 if (Type&TS_DTS)
1703 DTSb*=Frequency_c;
1704 }
1705 }
1706 else
1707 {
1708 if (!Frequency_c)
1709 return;
1710
1711 if (Type&TS_PTS)
1712 FrameInfo.PTSc=Ticks;
1713 if (Type&TS_DTS)
1714 FrameInfo.DTSc=Ticks;
1715 }
1716
1717 FrameInfo.Frame_Count_AfterLastTimeStamp=0;
1718#endif //MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
1719}

1740//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1741void File__Analyze::TS_Ajust(int64s Ticks)
1742{
1743#if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
1744 if (IsRawStream)
1745 {
1746 if (PTSb==NoTs)
1747 {
1748 if (FrameInfo.DTSc!=NoTs)
1749 PTSb=FrameInfo.DTSc*Frequency_b+Ticks*FrameInfo.Frame_Count_AfterLastTimeStamp*(Frequency_c?Frequency_c:1); // Relying on DTS only, ajustment is done by the function itself
1750 else
1751 PTSb=-Ticks*FrameInfo.Frame_Count_AfterLastTimeStamp*(Frequency_c?Frequency_c:1);
1752 }
1753
1754 if (PTSb!=NoTs)
1755 PTSb+=Ticks*(Frequency_c?Frequency_c:1);
1756 }
1757 else
1758 {
1759 if (PTSb!=NoTs)
1760 PTSb+=Ticks;
1761 }
1762#endif //MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2

1765//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1766void File__Analyze::TS_Add(int64s Ticks, ts_type Type)
1767{
1768 if (IsRawStream)
1769 {
1770 //Coherency test
1771 if (!Frequency_b)
1772 {
1773 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
1774 FrameInfo.Frame_Count_AfterLastTimeStamp++;
1775 #endif //MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
1776 return;
1777 }
1778
1779 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
1780 //Filling first TS if not set somewhere else
1781 if (Type&TS_PTS && PTSb==NoTs)
1782 {
1783 if (FrameInfo.PTSc!=NoTs)
1784 PTSb=FrameInfo.PTSc*Frequency_b+Ticks*FrameInfo.Frame_Count_AfterLastTimeStamp*(Frequency_c?Frequency_c:1);
1785 else
1786 PTSb=-Ticks*FrameInfo.Frame_Count_AfterLastTimeStamp*(Frequency_c?Frequency_c:1);
1787 }
1788 if (Type&TS_DTS && DTSb==NoTs)
1789 {
1790 if (FrameInfo.DTSc!=NoTs)
1791 DTSb=FrameInfo.DTSc*Frequency_b+Ticks*FrameInfo.Frame_Count_AfterLastTimeStamp*(Frequency_c?Frequency_c:1);
1792 else
1793 DTSb=-Ticks*FrameInfo.Frame_Count_AfterLastTimeStamp*(Frequency_c?Frequency_c:1);
1794 }
1795
1796 //Coherency test
1797 if (Type&TS_PTS && PTSb!=NoTs && FrameInfo.PTSc!=NoTs)
1798 {
1799 if (!FrameInfo.Frame_Count_AfterLastTimeStamp && PTSb != FrameInfo.PTSc*Frequency_b && (FrameInfo.PTSc*Frequency_b-PTSb<=-Frequency_b || FrameInfo.PTSc*Frequency_b-PTSb>=Frequency_b))
1800 {
1801 PTSb=FrameInfo.PTSc*Frequency_b;
1802 }
1803 }
1804 if (Type&TS_DTS && DTSb!=NoTs && FrameInfo.DTSc!=NoTs)
1805 {
1806 if (!FrameInfo.Frame_Count_AfterLastTimeStamp && DTSb != FrameInfo.DTSc*Frequency_b && (FrameInfo.DTSc*Frequency_b-DTSb<=-Frequency_b || FrameInfo.DTSc*Frequency_b-DTSb>=Frequency_b))
1807 {
1808 DTSb=FrameInfo.DTSc*Frequency_b;
1809 }
1810 }
1811 #endif //MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
1812 }
1813
1814 //Trace
1815 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
1816 Element_Info1(Ztring::ToZtring(Frame_Count));
1817 Element_Info1C((DTSb!=NoTs && DTSb!=PTSb), __T("DTS ")+Ztring().Duration_From_Milliseconds(float64_int64s(((float64)DTSb)*1000/(Frequency_c?Frequency_c:1)/Frequency_b)));
1818 Element_Info1C((PTSb!=NoTs), __T("PTS ")+Ztring().Duration_From_Milliseconds(float64_int64s(((float64)PTSb)*1000/(Frequency_c?Frequency_c:1)/Frequency_b)));
1819 #else //MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
1820 Element_Info1C((FrameInfo.DTS!=(int64u)-1 && FrameInfo.PTS!=(int64u)-1), __T("DTS ")+Ztring().Duration_From_Milliseconds(float64_int64s(((float64)FrameInfo.DTS)/1000000)));
1821 Element_Info1C((FrameInfo.PTS!=(int64u)-1), __T("PTS ")+Ztring().Duration_From_Milliseconds(float64_int64s(((float64)FrameInfo.PTS)/1000000)));
1822 Element_Info1(Frame_Count);
1823 #endif //MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
1824
1825 //Adding timestamp
1826 FrameInfo.DUR=Ticks*1000000000/Frequency_b;
1827 if (Type&TS_PTS && FrameInfo.PTS!=(int64u)-1 && Frequency_b)
1828 FrameInfo.PTS+=FrameInfo.DUR;
1829 if (Type&TS_DTS && FrameInfo.DTS!=(int64u)-1 && Frequency_b)
1830 FrameInfo.DTS+=FrameInfo.DUR;
1831 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
1832 if (IsRawStream)
1833 {
1834 if (Type&TS_PTS && PTSb!=NoTs)
1835 PTSb+=Ticks*(Frequency_c?Frequency_c:1);
1836 if (Type&TS_DTS && DTSb!=NoTs)
1837 DTSb+=Ticks*(Frequency_c?Frequency_c:1);
1838 }
1839 else
1840 {
1841 if (Type&TS_PTS && PTSb!=NoTs)
1842 PTSb+=Ticks;
1843 if (Type&TS_DTS && DTSb!=NoTs)
1844 DTSb+=Ticks;
1845 }
1846 FrameInfo.Frame_Count_AfterLastTimeStamp++;
1847 #endif //MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
1848 Frame_Count++;
1849 Frame_Count_InThisBlock++;
1850 if (Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded!=(int64u)-1)
1851 Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded++;
1852}

1854//***************************************************************************
1855// Synchro
1856//***************************************************************************
1857
1858//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1859bool File__Analyze::Synchro_Manage()
1860{
1861 //Testing if synchro is OK
1862 if (Synched)
1863 {
1864 if (!IsSub)
1865 Buffer_TotalBytes_LastSynched=Buffer_TotalBytes+Buffer_Offset;
1866
1867 if (!Synchro_Manage_Test())
1868 return false;
1869 }
1870
1871 //Trying to synchronize
1872 if (!Synched)
1873 {
1874 //Buffer_TotalBytes_Fill_Max
1875 if (!Status[IsFilled] && Buffer_TotalBytes>=Buffer_TotalBytes_Fill_Max)
1876 {
1877 Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
1878 GoToFromEnd(0);
1879 return false;
1880 }
1881 if (!Synchronize())
1882 {
1883 if (Status[IsFinished])
1884 Finish(); //Finish
1885 if (!IsSub && File_Offset_FirstSynched==(int64u)-1 && Buffer_TotalBytes+Buffer_Offset>=Buffer_TotalBytes_FirstSynched_Max)
1886 {
1887 Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
1888 GoToFromEnd(0);
1889 }
1890 return false; //Wait for more data
1891 }
1892 Synched=true;
1893 if (!IsSub)
1894 {
1895 if (!UnSynched_IsNotJunk)
1896 Buffer_JunkBytes+=Buffer_TotalBytes+Buffer_Offset-Buffer_TotalBytes_LastSynched;
1897 Buffer_TotalBytes_LastSynched=Buffer_TotalBytes+Buffer_Offset;
1898 UnSynched_IsNotJunk=false;
1899 }
1900 if (File_Offset_FirstSynched==(int64u)-1)
1901 {
1902 Synched_Init();
1903 Buffer_TotalBytes_FirstSynched+=Buffer_TotalBytes+Buffer_Offset;
1904 File_Offset_FirstSynched=File_Offset+Buffer_Offset;
1905 }
1906 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1907 if (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
1908 return false;
1909 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1910 if (!Synchro_Manage_Test())
1911 return false;
1912 }
1913
1914 return true;
1915}
1916
1917//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1918bool File__Analyze::Synchro_Manage_Test()
1919{
1920 //Testing if synchro is OK
1921 if (Synched)
1922 {
1923 if (!Synched_Test())
1924 return false;
1925 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1926 if (Synched && Demux_TotalBytes<=Buffer_TotalBytes+Buffer_Offset)
1927 {
1928 if (Demux_UnpacketizeContainer && !Demux_UnpacketizeContainer_Test())
1929 {
1930 Demux_Offset-=Buffer_Offset;
1931 return false; //Wait for more data
1932 }
1933 if (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
1934 return false;
1935 }
1936 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1937 if (Buffer_Offset>=FrameInfo.Buffer_Offset_End && FrameInfo_Next.DTS!=(int64u)-1)
1938 {
1939 FrameInfo=FrameInfo_Next;
1940 FrameInfo_Next=frame_info();
1941 }
1942 if (Synched)
1943 {
1944 if (!IsSub)
1945 Buffer_TotalBytes_LastSynched=Buffer_TotalBytes+Buffer_Offset;
1946 }
1947 else
1948 {
1949 Element[Element_Level].IsComplete=true; //Else the trusting algo will think it
1950 Trusted_IsNot("Synchronisation lost");
1951 while (Element_Level)
1952 Element_End();
1953 }
1954 }
1955
1956 //Trying to synchronize
1957 if (!Synched)
1958 {
1959 if (!Synchronize())
1960 {
1961 if (Status[IsFinished])
1962 Finish(); //Finish
1963 if (!IsSub && File_Offset_FirstSynched==(int64u)-1 && Buffer_TotalBytes+Buffer_Offset>=Buffer_TotalBytes_FirstSynched_Max)
1964 Reject();
1965 return false; //Wait for more data
1966 }
1967 Synched=true;
1968 if (!IsSub)
1969 {
1970 if (!UnSynched_IsNotJunk)
1971 Buffer_JunkBytes+=Buffer_TotalBytes+Buffer_Offset-Buffer_TotalBytes_LastSynched;
1972 Buffer_TotalBytes_LastSynched=Buffer_TotalBytes+Buffer_Offset;
1973 UnSynched_IsNotJunk=false;
1974 }
1975 if (File_Offset_FirstSynched==(int64u)-1)
1976 {
1977 Synched_Init();
1978 Buffer_TotalBytes_FirstSynched+=Buffer_TotalBytes+Buffer_Offset;
1979 File_Offset_FirstSynched=File_Offset+Buffer_Offset;
1980 }
1981 if (!Synched_Test())
1982 return false;
1983 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1984 if (Synched && Demux_TotalBytes<=Buffer_TotalBytes+Buffer_Offset)
1985 {
1986 if (Demux_UnpacketizeContainer && !Demux_UnpacketizeContainer_Test())
1987 {
1988 Demux_Offset-=Buffer_Offset;
1989 return false; //Wait for more data
1990 }
1991 if (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
1992 return false;
1993 }
1994 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1995 }
1996
1997 return true;
1998}

2000//***************************************************************************
2001// File Header
2002//***************************************************************************
2003
2004//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005bool File__Analyze::FileHeader_Manage()
2006{
2007 //From the parser
2008 if (!Status[IsAccepted] && !FileHeader_Begin())
2009 {
2010 if (Status[IsFinished]) //Newest parsers set this bool if there is an error
2011 Reject();
2012 if (File_Offset+Buffer_Size>=File_Size)
2013 Reject();
2014 return false; //Wait for more data
2015 }
2016
2017 //Positionning
2018 if ((Buffer_Size && Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset>Buffer_Size) || (sizeof(size_t)<sizeof(int64u) && Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset>=(int64u)(size_t)-1))
2019 {
2020 GoTo(File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset);
2021 return false;
2022 }
2023 else
2024 {
2025 Buffer_Offset+=(size_t)Element_Offset;
2026 Element_Offset=0;
2027 }
2028
2029 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
2030 if (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
2031 return false;
2032 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
2033
2034 //From the parser
2035 Element_Size=Buffer_Size-Buffer_Offset;
2036 Element_Begin1("File Header");
2037 FileHeader_Parse();
2038 if (Element_Offset==0)
2039 Element_DoNotShow();
2040 Element_End0();
2041 if (Status[IsFinished]) //Newest parsers set this bool if there is an error
2042 {
2043 Finish();
2044 return false;
2045 }
2046
2047 //Testing the parser result
2048 if (Element_IsWaitingForMoreData() || Element[Element_Level].UnTrusted) //Wait or problem
2049 {
2050 //The header is not complete, need more data
2051 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
2052 Element[Element_Level].TraceNode.Init();
2053 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
2054 return false;
2055 }
2056
2057 //Positionning
2058 if ((Buffer_Size && Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset>Buffer_Size) || (sizeof(size_t)<sizeof(int64u) && Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset>=(int64u)(size_t)-1))
2059 {
2060 GoTo(File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset);
2061 return false;
2062 }
2063 else
2064 {
2065 Buffer_Offset+=(size_t)Element_Offset;
2066 Element_Offset=0;
2067 }
2068
2069 MustParseTheHeaderFile=false;
2070 return true;
2071}

2073//***************************************************************************
2074// Header
2075//***************************************************************************
2076
2077//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2078bool File__Analyze::Header_Manage()
2079{
2080 //Test
2081 if (Buffer_Offset>=Buffer_Size)
2082 return false;
2083
2084 //Header begin
2085 Element_Size=Element[Element_Level].Next-(File_Offset+Buffer_Offset);
2086 Element_Offset=0;
2087 if (!Header_Begin())
2088 {
2089 //Jumping to the end of the file if needed
2090 if (!EOF_AlreadyDetected && Config->ParseSpeed<1 && File_GoTo==(int64u)-1)
2091 {
2092 Element[Element_Level].WaitForMoreData=false;
2093 Detect_EOF();
2094 if ((File_GoTo!=(int64u)-1 && File_GoTo>File_Offset+Buffer_Offset) || (Status[IsFinished] && !ShouldContinueParsing))
2095 EOF_AlreadyDetected=true;
2096 }
2097 return false; //Wait for more data
2098 }
2099
2100 //Going in a lower level
2101 Element_Size=Element[Element_Level].Next-(File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset);
2102 Element[Element_Level].UnTrusted=false;
2103 if (Buffer_Offset+Element_Size>Buffer_Size)
2104 {
2105 Element_Size=Buffer_Size-Buffer_Offset;
2106 Element[Element_Level].IsComplete=false;
2107 }
2108 else
2109 Element[Element_Level].IsComplete=true;
2110 if (Element_Size==0)
2111 return false;
2112 Element_Offset=0;
2113 Element_Begin0(); //Element
2114 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
2115 Data_Level=Element_Level;
2116 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
2117 Element_Begin1("Header"); //Header
2118
2119 //Header parsing
2120 Header_Parse();
2121
2122 //Testing the parser result
2123 if (Element[Element_Level].UnTrusted) //Problem
2124 {
2125 Element[Element_Level].UnTrusted=false;
2126 Header_Fill_Code(0, "Problem");
2127 if (MustSynchronize)
2128 {
2129 //Unsynchronizing to the next byte
2130 Element_Offset=1;
2131 Header_Fill_Size(1);
2132 Synched=false;
2133 }
2134 else
2135 {
2136 //Can not synchronize anymore in this block
2137 Element_Offset=Element[Element_Level-2].Next-(File_Offset+Buffer_Offset);
2138 Header_Fill_Size(Element_Offset);
2139 }
2140 }
2141
2142 if (Element_IsWaitingForMoreData() || ((DataMustAlwaysBeComplete && Element[Element_Level-1].Next>File_Offset+Buffer_Size) || File_GoTo!=(int64u)-1) //Wait or want to have a comple data chunk
2143 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
2144 || (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
2145 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
2146 )
2147 {
2148 //The header is not complete, need more data
2149 Element[Element_Level].WaitForMoreData=true;
2150 Element_End0(); //Header
2151 Element_End0(); //Element
2152 return false;
2153 }
2154
2155 //Filling
2156 Element[Element_Level].WaitForMoreData=false;
2157 Element[Element_Level].IsComplete=true;
2158
2159 //TraceNode
2160 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
2161 if (Trace_Activated)
2162 {
2163 if (!Element[Element_Level-1].TraceNode.Get_Name())
2164 Element[Element_Level-1].TraceNode.Set_Name("Unknown");
2165 Element[Element_Level].TraceNode.Size=Element_Offset;
2166 if (Element_Offset==0)
2167 Element_DoNotShow();
2168 }
2169 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
2170
2171 //Integrity
2172 if (Element[Element_Level-1].Next<(File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset))
2173 Element[Element_Level-1].Next=File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset; //Size is not good
2174
2175 //Positionning
2176 Element_Size=Element[Element_Level-1].Next-(File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset);
2177 Header_Size=Element_Offset;
2178 Buffer_Offset+=(size_t)Header_Size;
2179 Element_Offset=0;
2180 if (Buffer_Offset+Element_Size>Buffer_Size)
2181 {
2182 if (Buffer_Size>Buffer_Offset)
2183 Element_Size=Buffer_Size-Buffer_Offset;
2184 else
2185 Element_Size=0; //There is an error in the parsing
2186 Element[Element_Level-1].IsComplete=false;
2187 }
2188
2189 Element_End0(); //Header
2190 return true;
2191}

2193//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2194void File__Analyze::Header_Parse()
2195{
2196 //Filling
2197 Header_Fill_Code(0);
2198 Header_Fill_Size(Element_Size);
2199}

2224//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2225void File__Analyze::Header_Fill_Size(int64u Size)
2226{
2227 if (Size==0)
2228 Trusted_IsNot("Block can't have a size of 0");
2229 if (DataMustAlwaysBeComplete && Size>Buffer_MaximumSize)
2230 {
2231 Element[Element_Level].IsComplete=true;
2232 Element[Element_Level-1].IsComplete=true;
2233 Trusted_IsNot("Block is too big");
2234 }
2235
2236 if (Element[Element_Level].UnTrusted)
2237 return;
2238
2239 //Integrity
2240 if (Size<Element_Offset)
2241 Size=Element_Offset; //At least what we read before!!!
2242
2243 //Filling
2244 if (Element_Level==1)
2245 Element[0].Next=File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Size;
2246 else if (File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Size>Element[Element_Level-2].Next)
2247 Element[Element_Level-1].Next=Element[Element_Level-2].Next;
2248 else
2249 Element[Element_Level-1].Next=File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Size;
2250 Element[Element_Level-1].IsComplete=true;
2251
2252 //TraceNode
2253 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
2254 if (Trace_Activated)
2255 {
2256 Element[Element_Level-1].TraceNode.Pos=File_Offset+Buffer_Offset;
2257 Element[Element_Level-1].TraceNode.Size=Element[Element_Level-1].Next-(File_Offset+Buffer_Offset);
2258 }
2259 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
2260}

2262//***************************************************************************
2263// Data
2264//***************************************************************************
2265
2266//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2267bool File__Analyze::Data_Manage()
2268{
2269 Element_WantNextLevel=false;
2270 if (!Element[Element_Level].UnTrusted)
2271 {
2272 Element_Code=Element[Element_Level].Code;
2273 //size_t Element_Level_Save=Element_Level;
2274 Data_Parse();
2275 BS->Attach(NULL, 0); //Clear it
2276 //Element_Level=Element_Level_Save;
2277
2278 if (Buffer_Offset+(Element_WantNextLevel?Element_Offset:Element_Size)>=FrameInfo.Buffer_Offset_End)
2279 {
2280 if (Frame_Count_Previous<Frame_Count)
2281 Frame_Count_Previous=Frame_Count;
2282 if (Field_Count_Previous<Field_Count)
2283 Field_Count_Previous=Field_Count;
2284 }
2285
2286 if (Buffer_Offset+(Element_WantNextLevel?Element_Offset:Element_Size)>=FrameInfo.Buffer_Offset_End && FrameInfo_Next.DTS!=(int64u)-1)
2287 {
2288 FrameInfo=FrameInfo_Next;
2289 FrameInfo_Next=frame_info();
2290 }
2291
2292 //Testing the parser result
2293 if (Element_IsWaitingForMoreData())
2294 {
2295 //The data is not complete, need more data
2296 Element_End0(); //Element
2297 Buffer_Offset-=(size_t)Header_Size;
2298 return false;
2299 }
2300
2301 Element[Element_Level].IsComplete=true;
2302
2303 if (!Element_WantNextLevel && DataMustAlwaysBeComplete && Element_Offset<Element_Size)
2304 Element_Offset=Element_Size; //In case the element is not fully parsed, an element with size from the header is assumed
2305 }
2306
2307 //If no need of more
2308 if (File_GoTo!=(int64u)-1 || (Status[IsFinished] && !ShouldContinueParsing)
2309 #if MEDIAINFO_HASH
2310 || Hash_ParseUpTo
2311 #endif //MEDIAINFO_HASH
2312 )
2313 {
2314 if (!Element_WantNextLevel)
2315 Element_End0(); //Element
2316 if (!Element_WantNextLevel && Element_Offset<Element_Size)
2317 Buffer_Offset+=(size_t)Element_Size;
2318 else
2319 {
2320 if (sizeof(size_t)<sizeof(int64u) && Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset>=(int64u)(size_t)-1)
2321 GoTo(File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset);
2322 else
2323 Buffer_Offset+=(size_t)Element_Offset;
2324 }
2325 Header_Size=0;
2326 Element_Size=0;
2327 Element_Offset=0;
2328 return false;
2329 }
2330
2331 //Next element
2332 if (!Element_WantNextLevel
2333 #if MEDIAINFO_HASH
2334 && Hash==NULL
2335 #endif //MEDIAINFO_HASH
2336 )
2337 {
2338 if (Element[Element_Level].Next<=File_Offset+Buffer_Size)
2339 {
2340 if (Element_Offset<(size_t)(Element[Element_Level].Next-File_Offset-Buffer_Offset))
2341 Element_Offset=(size_t)(Element[Element_Level].Next-File_Offset-Buffer_Offset);
2342 }
2343 else if (!Status[IsFinished])
2344 {
2345 GoTo(Element[Element_Level].Next);
2346 if (!Element_WantNextLevel)
2347 Element_End0(); //Element
2348 return false;
2349 }
2350 }
2351
2352 if (!Element_WantNextLevel && Element_Offset<Element_Size)
2353 Buffer_Offset+=(size_t)Element_Size;
2354 else
2355 {
2356 if (sizeof(size_t)<sizeof(int64u) && Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset>=(int64u)(size_t)-1)
2357 GoTo(File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset);
2358 else
2359 Buffer_Offset+=(size_t)Element_Offset;
2360 }
2361 Header_Size=0;
2362 Element_Size=0;
2363 Element_Offset=0;
2364
2365 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
2366 if (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
2367 {
2368 if (!Element_WantNextLevel)
2369 Element_End0();
2370 return false;
2371 }
2372 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
2373
2374 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
2375 if (Element_Level>0)
2376 Element[Element_Level-1].TraceNode.NoShow=Element[Element_Level].TraceNode.NoShow; //If data must not be shown, we hide the header too
2377 else
2378 Element[0].TraceNode.NoShow=false; //This should never happen, but in case of
2379 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
2380 if (!Element_WantNextLevel)
2381 Element_End0(); //Element
2382 Element[Element_Level].UnTrusted=false;
2383
2384 //Jumping to the end of the file if needed
2385 if (!EOF_AlreadyDetected && Config->ParseSpeed<1 && File_GoTo==(int64u)-1)
2386 {
2387 Element[Element_Level].WaitForMoreData=false;
2388 Detect_EOF();
2389 if ((File_GoTo!=(int64u)-1 && File_GoTo>File_Offset+Buffer_Offset) || (Status[IsFinished] && !ShouldContinueParsing))
2390 {
2391 EOF_AlreadyDetected=true;
2392 return false;
2393 }
2394 }
2395
2396 return true;
2397}

2807#endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE

3002//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3003#if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
3004void File__Analyze::ForceFinish (const char* ParserName_Char)
3005#else //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
3006void File__Analyze::ForceFinish ()
3007#endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
3008{
3009 if (Status[IsFinished])
3010 return;
3011
3012 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
3013 if (ParserName.empty() && ParserName_Char)
3014 ParserName = ParserName_Char;
3015
3016 if (!ParserName.empty())
3017 {
3018 bool MustElementBegin=Element_Level?true:false;
3019 if (Element_Level>0)
3020 Element_End0(); //Element
3021 Info(ParserName+", finished");
3022 if (MustElementBegin)
3023 Element_Level++;
3024 }
3025 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
3026
3027 if (Status[IsAccepted])
3028 {
3029 //Total file size
3030 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
3031 if (!IsSub && !(!Config->File_IgnoreSequenceFileSize_Get() || Config->File_Names.size()<=1) && Config->ParseSpeed>=1.0 && Config->File_Names.size()>1 && Config->File_Names_Pos+1>=Config->File_Names.size())
3032 {
3033 Fill (Stream_General, 0, General_FileSize, Config->File_Current_Size, 10, true);
3034 }
3035 #endif //MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
3036
3037 Fill();
3038 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
3039 if (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
3040 return;
3041 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
3042 Streams_Finish();
3043 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
3044 if (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
3045 return;
3046 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
3047 if (Status[IsUpdated])
3048 {
3049 Open_Buffer_Update();
3050 if (IsSub)
3051 Status[IsUpdated]=true; //We want that container merges the result
3052 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
3053 if (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
3054 return;
3055 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
3056 }
3057 Streams_Finish_Global();
3058 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
3059 if (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
3060 return;
3061 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
3062 Ibi_Stream_Finish();
3063 }
3064
3065 Status[IsFinished]=true;
3066
3067 //Real stream size
3068 if (Config->ParseSpeed==1 && IsRawStream && Buffer_TotalBytes)
3069 {
3070 //Exception with text streams embedded in video
3071 if (StreamKind_Last==Stream_Text)
3072 StreamKind_Last=Stream_Video;
3073
3074 Fill(StreamKind_Last, 0, "StreamSize", Buffer_TotalBytes, 10, true);
3075 }
3076
3077 //Frame count
3078 if (Config->ParseSpeed==1 && IsRawStream && Frame_Count && Frame_Count!=(int64u)-1 && Retrieve(StreamKind_Last, 0, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind_Last, Generic_FrameCount)).empty())
3079 Fill(StreamKind_Last, 0, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind_Last, Generic_FrameCount), Frame_Count);
3080}

3433//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3434void File__Analyze::BookMark_Set (size_t Element_Level_ToSet)
3435{
3436 Element_Level_ToSet=Element_Level;
3437 BookMark_Element_Level=Element_Level_ToSet;
3438 BookMark_Code.resize(BookMark_Element_Level+1);
3439 BookMark_Next.resize(BookMark_Element_Level+1);
3440 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<=BookMark_Element_Level; Pos++)
3441 {
3442 BookMark_Code[Pos]=Element[Pos].Code;
3443 BookMark_Next[Pos]=Element[Pos].Next;
3444 }
3445 BookMark_GoTo=File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset;
3446}

3448//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3449void File__Analyze::BookMark_Get ()
3450{
3451 if (!BookMark_Needed())
3452 return;
3453
3454 Element_Show();
3455 while (Element_Level>0)
3456 Element_End0();
3457 while (Element_Level<BookMark_Element_Level)
3458 {
3459 Element_Begin1("Restarting parsing...");
3460 Element_WantNextLevel=true;
3461 }
3462
3463 if (!BookMark_Code.empty())
3464 {
3465 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<=BookMark_Element_Level; Pos++)
3466 {
3467 Element[Pos].Code=BookMark_Code[Pos];
3468 Element[Pos].Next=BookMark_Next[Pos];
3469 }
3470 BookMark_Code.clear();
3471 BookMark_Next.clear();
3472 BookMark_Element_Level=0;
3473 }
3474 if (File_GoTo==(int64u)-1)
3475 {
3476 #if MEDIAINFO_HASH
3477 delete Hash; Hash=NULL;
3478 #endif //MEDIAINFO_HASH
3479 File_GoTo=BookMark_GoTo;
3480 }

3514void File__Analyze::Demux (const int8u* Buffer, size_t Buffer_Size, contenttype Content_Type, const int8u* xx, size_t xxx)
3515{
3516 if (!(Config_Demux&Demux_Level))
3517 return;
3518
3519 if (!Buffer_Size)
3520 return;
3521
3522 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX && MEDIAINFO_SEEK
3523 if (Config->Demux_IsSeeking)
3524 return;
3525 #endif //MEDIAINFO_SEEK
3526
3527 #if MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
3528 //Demux
3529 if (StreamIDs_Size)
3530 StreamIDs[StreamIDs_Size-1]=Element_Code;
3531
3532 EVENT_BEGIN(Global, Demux, 4)
3533 if (StreamIDs_Size)
3534 Event.EventCode|=((int32u)ParserIDs[StreamIDs_Size-1]<<24);
3535 Event.Content_Type=(int8u)Content_Type;
3536 Event.Content_Size=Buffer_Size;
3537 Event.Content=Buffer;
3538 Event.Flags=0;
3539 if (Demux_random_access)
3540 Event.Flags|=0x1; //Bit 0
3541 Event.Offsets_Size=Offsets_Buffer.size();
3542 std::vector<int64u> Offsets_Stream_Temp;
3543 std::vector<int64u> Offsets_Buffer_Temp;
3544 float64 Ratio=1;
3545 if (OriginalBuffer_Size)
3546 Ratio=((float64)File__Analyze::OriginalBuffer_Size)/File__Analyze::Buffer_Size;
3547 if (Offsets_Buffer.empty())
3548 {
3549 Event.Offsets_Stream=NULL;
3550 Event.Offsets_Content=NULL;
3551 }
3552 else if (Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset)
3553 {
3554 Offsets_Stream_Temp=Offsets_Stream;
3555 Offsets_Buffer_Temp=Offsets_Buffer;
3556 size_t Pos=0;
3557 if (Offsets_Buffer.size()>=2 && Offsets_Buffer.size()%2==0 && Offsets_Buffer[0]==Offsets_Buffer[1])
3558 {
3559 while (Pos+2<Offsets_Buffer_Temp.size() && Offsets_Buffer_Temp[Pos+2]<Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset)
3560 Pos+=2;
3561 if (Pos)
3562 {
3563 Offsets_Buffer_Temp.erase(Offsets_Buffer_Temp.begin(), Offsets_Buffer_Temp.begin()+Pos);
3564 Offsets_Stream_Temp.erase(Offsets_Stream_Temp.begin(), Offsets_Stream_Temp.begin()+Pos);
3565 Event.Offsets_Size-=Pos;
3566 }
3567 Offsets_Stream_Temp[0]+=(Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset)/2-Offsets_Buffer_Temp[0];
3568 Offsets_Stream_Temp[1]+=(Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset)/2-Offsets_Buffer_Temp[1];
3569 Offsets_Buffer_Temp[0]=0;
3570 Offsets_Buffer_Temp[1]=0;
3571 for (size_t Pos=2; Pos<Offsets_Buffer_Temp.size(); Pos+=2)
3572 {
3573 Offsets_Buffer_Temp[Pos]-=(Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset)/2;
3574 Offsets_Buffer_Temp[Pos+1]-=(Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset)/2;
3575 }
3576 }
3577 else
3578 {
3579 while (Pos+1<Offsets_Buffer_Temp.size() && Offsets_Buffer_Temp[Pos+1]<(Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset)*Ratio)
3580 Pos++;
3581 if (Pos)
3582 {
3583 Offsets_Buffer_Temp.erase(Offsets_Buffer_Temp.begin(), Offsets_Buffer_Temp.begin()+Pos);
3584 Offsets_Stream_Temp.erase(Offsets_Stream_Temp.begin(), Offsets_Stream_Temp.begin()+Pos);
3585 Event.Offsets_Size-=Pos;
3586 }
3587 Offsets_Stream_Temp[0]+=float64_int64s((Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset)*Ratio)-Offsets_Buffer_Temp[0];
3588 Offsets_Buffer_Temp[0]=0;
3589 for (size_t Pos=1; Pos<Offsets_Buffer_Temp.size(); Pos++)
3590 Offsets_Buffer_Temp[Pos]-=float64_int64s((Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset)*Ratio);
3591 }
3592 Event.Offsets_Stream=&Offsets_Stream_Temp.front();
3593 Event.Offsets_Content=&Offsets_Buffer_Temp.front();
3594 }
3595 else
3596 {
3597 Event.Offsets_Stream=&Offsets_Stream.front();
3598 Event.Offsets_Content=&Offsets_Buffer.front();
3599 }
3600 Event.OriginalContent_Size=OriginalBuffer_Size?((size_t)float64_int64s(((float64)(Element_Size-Element_Offset))*Ratio)):0;
3601 Event.OriginalContent=OriginalBuffer_Size?(OriginalBuffer+(size_t)float64_int64s(((float64)(Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset))*Ratio)):NULL;
3602 EVENT_END()
3603
3604 if (StreamIDs_Size)
3605 StreamIDs[StreamIDs_Size-1]=(int64u)-1;
3606 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX && MEDIAINFO_NEXTPACKET
3607 if (Status[IsAccepted] && Config->NextPacket_Get())
3608 Config->Demux_EventWasSent=true;
3609 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX && MEDIAINFO_NEXTPACKET
3610 if (StreamIDs_Size)
3611 StreamIDs[StreamIDs_Size-1]=(int64u)-1;
3612 #endif //MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
3613}
3614#endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX

3876void File__Analyze::Ibi_Stream_Finish ()
3877{
3878 if (IsSub)
3879 return;
3880
3881 if (!(IbiStream==NULL || IbiStream->Infos.empty()) && File_Offset+Buffer_Size==File_Size)
3882 {
3883 ibi::stream::info IbiInfo;
3884 IbiInfo.StreamOffset=File_Offset+Buffer_Size;
3885 IbiInfo.FrameNumber=Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded;
3886 IbiInfo.Dts=(FrameInfo.DTS!=(int64u)-1)?float64_int64s(((float64)FrameInfo.DTS)/1000000000*IbiStream->DtsFrequencyNumerator/IbiStream->DtsFrequencyDenominator):(int64u)-1;
3887 IbiInfo.IsContinuous=true;
3888 IbiStream->Add(IbiInfo);
3889 }
3890
3891 if (Config_Ibi_Create)
3892 {
3893 if (!(IbiStream==NULL || IbiStream->Infos.empty()))
3894 Ibi.Streams[(int64u)-1]=new ibi::stream(*IbiStream);
3895
3896 //Inform_Data
3897 ZtringListList Content;
3898 for (size_t StreamKind=Stream_General; StreamKind<Stream_Max; ++StreamKind)
3899 {
3900 ZtringListList Source=MediaInfoLib::Config.Info_Get((stream_t)StreamKind);
3901
3902 for (size_t StreamPos=0; StreamPos<Count_Get((stream_t)StreamKind); ++StreamPos)
3903 {
3904 ZtringList KindAndPos;
3905 KindAndPos.push_back(Get((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, __T("StreamKind")));
3906 Content.push_back(KindAndPos);
3907
3908 //Standard
3909 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Source.size(); ++Pos)
3910 {
3911 Ztring &Options=Source[Pos](Info_Options);
3912 if (InfoOption_ShowInSupported<Options.size() && Options[InfoOption_ShowInSupported]==__T('Y') && Pos<(*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos].size() && !(*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos][Pos].empty())
3913 {
3914 ZtringList Line;
3915 Line.push_back(Source[Pos][Info_Name]);
3916 Line.push_back((*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos][Pos]);
3917 Content.push_back(Line);
3918 }
3919 }
3920
3921 //Additional
3922 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<(*Stream_More)[StreamKind][StreamPos].size(); ++Pos)
3923 {
3924 ZtringList Line=(*Stream_More)[StreamKind][StreamPos][Pos];
3925 Line.resize(Info_Options+1);
3926 Content.push_back(Line);
3927 }
3928
3929 //Separator
3930 Content.push_back(Ztring());
3931 }
3932 }
3933 if (!Content.empty())
3934 Content.resize(Content.size()-1);
3935 Ibi.Inform_Data=Content.Read();
3936
3937 //IBI Creation
3938 File_Ibi_Creation IbiCreation(Ibi);
3939 Ztring IbiText=IbiCreation.Finish();
3940 if (!IbiText.empty())
3941 {
3942 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "IBI", IbiText);
3943 (*Stream_More)[Stream_General][0]("IBI", Info_Options)=__T("N NT");
3944 }
3945 }
